{
  "texts": [
    "As a typical Gen AI solution, ChatGPT can offer benefits in multiple domains.",
    "This LLM (GPT-3.5 or GPT-4) is based on a general data set, which means that it leverages large quantities of publicly available data that provide a broad scope of source material for creating novel output.",
    "Therefore, ChatGPT could be used to create novel social media content and generate unique services or sales scripts (Sinha et al., 2023) based on a large body of unstructured information.",
    "In our discussions, the CEO of a technology start-up highlighted the use of Gen AI by both the marketing and technology departments.",
    "Specifically, the marketing department leveraged ChatGPT to craft new social media content, substantially improving productivity."
  ]
}